<br>
I'm going to post the list here.  If anyone feels like a guild member should have one of these items, instead of whatever person happens to show up at the riddle contest, please say so and I can always run that item to Ealwen.  Then we can work something out.<br>
<br>
Here's the list:<br>
<br>
Donated by Zulu:<br>
Sarnak Emblazoned Tabard<br>
Obsidian Ring<br>
Polished Granite Tomahawk<br>
Trueshot Longbow<br>
<br>
Donated by Tchallar:<br>
Fine Steel Morningstar (2)<br>
Wooden Totem<br>
Dagger of Dropping<br>
Fine Steel Longsword<br>
<br>
I also have five plat left over from the 100 Hama gave me to give newbies today at the First Aid Camp, and 26 rat whiskers <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Some of the items Zulu gave us are pretty high end.  I would be willing to give those to Ealwen for the guild treasury; perhaps we could have a more difficult event?<br>
<br>
In any event, this is a lot of stuff and I need y'all's input on what to do with it, so please post here or email me at gwion_the_druid@hotmail.com.<br>
<br>
Gracias,<br>
 <p>Gwion Llewellyn<BR> Level, um, 20 <BR> Convicted Drive-by Newbie Levitator</p><i>Edited by <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/ugwion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gwion</A> at: 9/4/00 5:06:05 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Kizor</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#006400>(9/5/00 9:02:02 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   The Goods</span><hr size=1> I'd like the Obsidian ring  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   i hate askin for stuff makes me feel so incredibly selfish.<br>
